Star Wars fans will have plenty to be happy about this year.

As well a brand new movie in the form of The Last Jedi - releasing this Christmas - there's also some gaming action on the horizon with Star Wars Battlefront 2.

The hotly anticipated title is a follow-up to the 2015 online multiplayer shooter from EA, itself a reboot of the Star Wars: Battlefront series
